song_name: Did I Say That Out Loud
Did I Say That Out Loud

version_description: All sections expanded out in full to enable scrolling entire song with all chords for live performance.
No chord affectations: a guide for solos, playing acoustic guitar / ukelele etc. A vibrant but gentle harmony for accompanied vocal melodies.

I transposed the original key to Capo 3 because I think it sounds better. I like the Bm and F# in barre chords so I can mute them as I'm strumming it. This also makes the rest of the chords open. Furthermore, I think there are a bunch of chords missing from the other versions.
